# ⚡ LinemanSafe — HESCOM Lineman Safety Portal

> A digital check-in/check-out system that protects electrical linemen working on live lines — preventing accidental power restoration and saving lives across Karnataka.

🔗 **Live Demo:** https://lineman-safe-production.up.railway.app

---

## 🎯 Problem Statement

HESCOM (Hubli Electricity Supply Company Limited) linemen risk their lives every day working on live electrical lines across 7 districts of Karnataka. The biggest danger — someone restoring power while a lineman is still on the pole.

Currently, shutdown coordination happens over **phone calls and word of mouth** — no digital record, no verification, no accountability.

This project was inspired by real incidents witnessed at HESCOM, including fatalities caused by poor communication during line maintenance.

---

## 💡 Solution

LinemanSafe is a **pure software solution** — no IoT devices required. Just a phone and internet connection.

```
Lineman opens app → logs in → clicks "Going Up"
         ↓
System LOCKS the line in database
         ↓
Supervisor sees RED ALERT on dashboard
         ↓
Lineman finishes work → clicks "I am Down Safely"
         ↓
System UNLOCKS the line → power can be restored
```

