## 🗄️ Database Schema

```sql
linemen        — Lineman accounts (employee ID, phone, password)
supervisors    — Supervisor accounts
lines          — All electrical lines (line code, area, district)
jobs           — Every work session (who, which line, when)
incidents      — SOS alerts and emergencies
```

---

## 🔌 API Endpoints

### Auth
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---|---|---|
| POST | `/api/auth/register-lineman` | Register new lineman |
| POST | `/api/auth/login-lineman` | Lineman login → JWT token |
| POST | `/api/auth/register-supervisor` | Register supervisor |
| POST | `/api/auth/login-supervisor` | Supervisor login → JWT token |

### Jobs
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---|---|---|
| POST | `/api/jobs/start` | Lineman going UP → locks line |
| POST | `/api/jobs/complete` | Lineman DOWN safely → unlocks line |
| POST | `/api/jobs/sos` | Emergency SOS alert |
| GET | `/api/jobs/active` | All active jobs |

### Lines
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---|---|---|
| GET | `/api/lines` | All lines with status |
| GET | `/api/lines/locked` | Currently locked lines |
| GET | `/api/lines/sos-alerts` | All SOS incidents |
| GET | `/api/lines/completed-jobs` | Recent completed jobs |
| POST | `/api/lines/add` | Add new line |

