## 🚀 Run Locally

### Prerequisites
- Node.js v18+
- PostgreSQL

### Setup

```bash
# Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/Preeti0810-ap/lineman-safe.git
cd lineman-safe

# Install dependencies
npm install

# Create .env file
cp .env.example .env
# Fill in your PostgreSQL credentials

# Create database tables
psql -U postgres -d lineman_safe -f schema.sql

# Start development server
npm run dev
```

Server runs at `http://localhost:3000`

