## ✨ Key Features

- ✅ **Digital line locking** — line cannot be re-energised while lineman is on pole
- ✅ **JWT authentication** — secure login for linemen and supervisors
- ✅ **One-tap SOS** — full screen red emergency alert, no typing needed
- ✅ **Live supervisor dashboard** — auto-refreshes every 3 seconds
- ✅ **Complete audit trail** — every job recorded with timestamps
- ✅ **GPS location tracking** — supervisor knows where lineman is
- ✅ **Mobile responsive** — works on any device in the field
- ✅ **HESCOM official design** — Karnataka government portal style

